# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/

# Per-account browser cookies + Chromium profiles for the web-search scraper.
# Each account has its own dir under accounts/<name>/ — both cookie.py
# (sid_guard etc.) and playwright_profile/ (logged-in session) must never
# be committed.
accounts/

# Old (pre-multi-account) layout. Kept in .gitignore so a stale local copy
# doesn't accidentally get committed during the migration.
web_cookie.py
.playwright_profile/

# Stray local-only files
*.log

# OLD/ — archived mobile/Frida/Waydroid scraper. Sensitive bits inside:
#   - OLD/libs/libmetasec_ov.so       (1.8MB extracted ByteDance binary)
#   - OLD/ttapk/*.apk                 (TT Lite redistribution risk)
#   - OLD/replay_search_vm*.py        (per-VM cookies + tokens)
#   - OLD/HISTORICAL/data/            (oracles, captured flows, traces)
OLD/libs/libmetasec_ov.so
OLD/ttapk/*.apk
OLD/replay_search_vm*.py
OLD/HISTORICAL/data/
